timeline.bodyText:
I would use a Builder pattern:
public static Builder newBuilder(Sampler root)

Where Builder allows to set any other Sampler. this way user don't have to configure all the others default samplers.

replies.bodyText:
@anuraaga Gotcha 👍 thanks. what about this?
parentBased(Sampler root)
parentBasedBuilder(Sampler root)

